{"tid":2131824,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"Buffon 退休先定係方國珊唔再參選立法會先","createTime":"2020-07-30T05:52:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T08:17:29.000Z","uid":154406,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"91c237dc2199e5db14a1aa2ac5c0c352c475fe79","tid":2131824,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T05:52:22.000Z","msg":"立法會選舉原定於 9 月 6 日舉行，近日有傳政府有意延期選舉一年。西貢區議員方國珊今日（29 日）在 FB 宣布參選 2020 新界東立法會選舉，質疑當市民要求封關時，政府及建制派沒遠見預先做事，反而在立法會選舉前「又突然患上『遠視』」。<br />\n<br />\n方國珊又指，泛民舉辦初選期間是第三波疫症爆發初期，他們沒有作防疫呼籲，認為「泛民其實都唔好得去邊」，批評泛民、建制派及政府都是「偽善者」，以政治利益行先&hellip;"},{"pid":"f56b97f33ea1bf7438bf4c071627ddcf6750a678","tid":2131824,"uid":38189,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T05:55:19.000Z","msg":"保方5屆世界盃 國山5屆立法會"},{"pid":"eba3c4946b76a98ce9640cf55b705b7e1401468e","tid":2131824,"uid":94501,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T05:56:05.000Z","msg":"Buffon 參選立法會先"},{"pid":"0e39ad120a4f8e7237659ad8102e6a1027e31d62","tid":2131824,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T05:57:21.000Z","msg":"孝義⋯"},{"pid":"c609bb0ea103e00fdf63fe06a49988a5d4ac0198","tid":2131824,"uid":22242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T05:58:10.000Z","msg":"宮崎駿退休先"},{"pid":"60e6ffd735e42a7c3ef5b2807b89e99700c45292","tid":2131824,"uid":202348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:06:10.000Z","msg":"宋楚瑜死先"},{"pid":"69d5ca755a0d86587ab502ee952858e49044bdda","tid":2131824,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60e6ffd735e42a7c3ef5b2807b89e99700c45292","tid":2131824,"uid":202348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:06:10.000Z","msg":"宋楚瑜死先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:31:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a643ca3907440f094c9191a3eacbd497dfd51cf6","tid":2131824,"uid":154406,"like":1,"dislike":0,